abstract: As Notre Dame's expected search for a new coach becomes the biggest story in college sports, the athletic director Jack Swarbrick is in the spotlight.
snippet: As Notre Dame's expected search for a new coach becomes the biggest story in college sports, the athletic director Jack Swarbrick is in the spotlight.
lead_paragraph: SOUTH BEND, Ind.  As dusk gave way to darkness here Saturday night, Athletic Director Jack Swarbrick sang the alma mater on the field at Notre Dame Stadium in the aftermath of the Fighting Irish’s double-overtime loss to UConn.

abstract: In asking for a replay, Ireland cite a 2005 match between Uzbekistan and Bahrain that was ordered to be repayed
snippet: In asking for a replay, Ireland cite a 2005 match between Uzbekistan and Bahrain that was ordered to be repayed
lead_paragraph: Seeking justice, and a spot in the World Cup in South Africa, the Football Association of Ireland has demanded a replay of the playoff with France, which ended in France’s favor after Thierry Henry handled the ball before passing to William Gallas for the score.
headline_main: Ireland Cites Uzbekistan-Bahrain Decision in Appeal
